data.description: This sweet Cape Cod is larger than it looks and located on corner lot for additional space and privacy! Spacious room sizes and hardwood floors throughout the home with 2 bedrooms & full bath on main and 2 bedrooms upstairs with 1/2 bath off master. Bedrooms have nice closets, updates & neutral palettes. Open concept dining/ kitchen with stainless appliances, granite countertops, newer cabinets,  and updated lighting. The bright and cheerful living room is full of natural light and a coat closet.The character remains throughout the home with the original woodwork, doors  and glass door knobs. Full basement with washer & dryer included and high ceilings for those wanting to finish. The sunroom/mud room off the kitchen is an extra bonus! Enhancements since 2017: new 28' rear deck, replaced roof/gutters/facia/,installed new drains in basement, new trex railing and front door, also updated paint and lighting. Fenced in yard for safety. Off street parking for 4 vehicles Location is prime!
